OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FThe son of a couple from East Sussex
OL,8,Fwho've been imprisoned in Iran since
OL,9,Fthe beginning of last year says his
OL,10,Ffamily was left in "sheer panic" after
OL,11,Fdiscovering that the US and Israel had
OL,12,Flaunched attacks on the Middle East.
OL,14,FLindsay and Craig Foreman were
OL,15,Fsentenced to 10 years in prison
OL,16,Ffollowing their arrest in January last
OL,17,Fyear while on their around-the-world
OL,18,Fmotorcycle trip.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FThe couple were arrested and taken
OL,8,Finto custody, before being charged
OL,9,Fwith espionage - something their
OL,10,Ffamily deny.
OL,12,FThey are currently being held in Evin
OL,13,Fprison, around 18km from the capital
OL,14,FTehran.
OL,16,FLindsay's son Joe says explosions
OL,17,Fheard in the background of their phone
OL,18,Fcall, left his mother petrified.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian Mr Bennett
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's like a pit in the stomach,
OL,9,Fyou don't feel it's real.
OL,11,F"It heightens the anxiety because your
OL,12,Floved ones are at the centre of it,
OL,13,Fyou know, they're at harm's risk."
OL,15,FJoe managed to speak to his mother
OL,16,FLindsay on Sunday, but said she was in
OL,17,F"a pure state of panic and hysteria"
OL,18,Fdue to hearing explosions nearby.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"It was horrible, because at that
OL,8,Fmoment you don't know what to say or
OL,9,Fdo," Joe added.
OL,11,F"You've just got to say, 'it's going
OL,12,Fto be okay, stay strong, it's going to
OL,13,Fbe okay, stay on the phone', and then
OL,14,Fthe phone goes - your mind loses
OL,15,Fitself.
OL,17,F"I managed to speak to Craig, and you
OL,18,Ffind out that the bombs are hitting
OL,19,Fclose enough that they're blowing out
OL,20,Fthe windows.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"It's very hard to deal with, but I've
OL,8,Fsaid this before, and I try and stay
OL,9,Fas composed as possible.
OL,11,F"They're the ones that are living
OL,12,Fthrough this.
OL,14,F"It's a hell of a worrying time for
OL,15,Fme, but I can't imagine what it must
OL,16,Fbe for them living through that
OL,17,Fexperience."
OL,19,FJoe says the Government have been good
OL,20,Fat listening to the family's concerns,
OL,21,Fbut overall he feels let down.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FReferring to Parliament he added:
OL,8,F"When you're talking about Iran, I
OL,9,Fneed to know that it's up on your
OL,10,Fagenda, that it's high on your list of
OL,11,Fpriorities.
OL,13,F"It's not going to be the highest, I
OL,14,Fappreciate that, but at least if it's
OL,15,Fin there and it's thought about, it
OL,16,Fgives us comfort that their name's
OL,17,Fbeing discussed and it gives them the
OL,18,Fstrength and knowledge that yes, okay,
OL,19,Fthe UK government care and they're
OL,20,Facting."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FEarlier this week, ITV News spoke to
OL,8,FRichard Radcliffe and his wife Nazanin
OL,9,FZaghari Radcliffe, who endured five
OL,10,Fyears in a Tehran prison after being
OL,11,Farrested..
OL,13,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe, a British-
OL,14,FIranian dual citizen, was arrested in
OL,15,F2016 on charges of plotting to
OL,16,Foverthrow the government during a
OL,17,Fvisit to her parents with her 22-month-
OL,18,Fold daughter Gabriella.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FHer husband, Richard, fought
OL,8,Ftirelessly to bring his wife back to
OL,9,FBritain after years of campaigning. Ms
OL,10,FZaghari-Ratcliffe was finally freed in
OL,11,FMarch 2022.
OL,13,FShe said she had been "unsettled" ever
OL,14,Fsince hearing the news of US-Israel
OL,15,Fstrikes on Saturday, adding: "I put
OL,16,Fsome podcast on and I went and sat at
OL,17,Fmy sewing machine. That's what makes
OL,18,Fme really calm down and focus."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FAfter hearing about Khamenei's
OL,8,Freported death from a friend, Ms
OL,9,FZaghari-Ratcliffe described feeling
OL,10,F"in shock" and disbelieving of whether
OL,11,For not it was confirmed.
OL,13,FNazanin has also been speaking to Mr
OL,14,FBennett about Craig and Lindsay's
OL,15,Fexperience.
OL,17,F"They're the only sign of hope,
OL,18,Freally, because Nazanin did come home
OL,19,Fand they understand what we've been
OL,20,Fthrough," Joe said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"Since speaking to them, they've made
OL,8,Fthe world of difference because it's
OL,9,Fjust a comforting thing to know that,
OL,10,Fokay, it is a tremendously difficult
OL,11,Ftime for both sides, but also that it
OL,12,Fdoes come to an end, that there is an
OL,13,Fend line and a finish line and your
OL,14,Floved ones do come home."
OL,16,FA FCDO spokesperson said: "The welfare
OL,17,Fof British nationals detained in Iran
OL,18,Fis a priority for this government and
OL,19,Fcontinues to be during the current
OL,20,Fsituation in the Middle East.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
