OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772651488
OL,3,CFamily of couple detained in Iran
OL,4,Cdescribes 'panic' after US-Israeli
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"We have been clear that Craig and
OL,8,FLindsay's sentences are completely
OL,9,Fappalling and totally unjustifiable,
OL,10,Fand we will continue to pursue this
OL,11,Fcase relentlessly with the Iranian
OL,12,Fgovernment and will do so until we see
OL,13,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman safely
OL,14,Freturned to the UK and reunited with
OL,15,Ftheir family.
OL,17,F"We continue to provide consular
OL,18,Fassistance to them and their family."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
